Class Procedure

  • java.lang.Object
    • ca.uhn.fhir.model.api.BaseElement
      • ca.uhn.fhir.model.api.BaseResource
        • ca.uhn.fhir.model.dstu.resource.Procedure
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    ICompositeElement, IElement, IResource, ISupportsUndeclaredExtensions

    public class Procedure
extends BaseResource
implements IResource
    HAPI/FHIR Procedure Resource (An action that is performed on a patient)

    Definition: An action that is performed on a patient. This can be a physical 'thing' like an operation, or less invasive like counseling or hypnotherapy

    Requirements:

    Profile Definition: http://hl7.org/fhir/profiles/Procedure
